<dataqual>
	<logic>The dataset is converted to file geodatabase (FGDB) format using tools in ArcGIS. The geometry is checked, and if needed repaired. The data set is created directly from a topologically correct ArcInfo coverage.</logic>
	<complete>After processing, the dataset is checked for drawing display and number of records and file sizes compared with source materials.</complete>
